[color=yellow]NOTES:[/color]

IMAGiNE bringing you another release.....The A-Team 2010 TS V2

OK sources used relizlab video and some sweet line audio from TA ,thanks to both :)
Also a special mention to 66Butch for syncing this one ,cheers bro  ;-)
Now why a v2???because we always do a v2 :lol: ,well the real reason is because we spent all morning creating
our own subpack for this....so now all non english parts have hardcoded english subs ;-)
Also we slightly changed the filtering and AR......firstly the AR,nothing wrong really with our first one but this res on this
only gives you a 0.1% AR error compared to 0.9% on the other ....so no major difference really.
The filtering....well we tried to make it a touch sharper and also remove some of that yellow.

Anyway this is for those that wanted a subbed version.......enjoy you fool!!
